description: For sale: $229,900. Waterfront home with level elevation to Hill Lake. One level living with four bedrooms - one is a master suite with a walk-in closet. Kitchen has an abundance of cabinets and counter top space, and main floor laundry nearby. Space galore with a living room and a separate family room with a patio door that leads to its own deck. Massive sized heated garage has its own partial bathroom, automobile lift run from an air compressor, concrete apron out front and to the side, and an asphalt drive to the road. Garage is electric in-floor heat. 1/4 bath is in garage.

description:
For sale: $425,000. One of a Kind !  An Up North, Country Home, Hobby Farm, Estate. Call it what you like.  20 miles from Grand Rapids, Minnesota.     Quiet - neighbors are close but not too close.
42.93 acres offered, made up of the 2 right hand parcels in the main photo.    All of the buildings sit within a 20 acre area.  We will sell it in pieces.   
 Want to talk?  Call  Joe  218 244 9232 
A great vacation home or live here year around - we do!
About 1 mile to Hill lake landing.  Snowmobile and golf in your own yard.  Lots of storage and garage space. Store your toys here - indoors!  
No need to haul them back and forth.  Horses? Fly in? Deer hunt from your own deck.  This is a must see property!  Spectacular  property w/ custom home built in 1999 - 2000, offering panoramic views of sunrises & sunsets. This 5 Bdrm, 3 full baths, 3600 sq ft home offers high end amenities throughout. The property offers several large out buildings for all your toys or possibly a business opportunity. Great for family getaways, hunting or corporate events. Adjacent to State land & miles of trails. Abundant wildlife for excellent hunting opportunities. Breathtaking views from every vantage point. A new roof in 2016. Main level great room design with vaulted ceiling for entertaining, 360 degree view of land with deck on all 4 sides, Granite counter tops, Custom natural finished Oak cabinets throughout home, Oak hardwood floors in great room, Beautiful main level field stone fireplace with granite hearth, Tile flooring in all bathrooms, Huge laundry and mud room, Heated in ground pool with updated high efficient heater, Master suite with large walk in closet, Master bath with separate walk in shower and whirlpool tub, Walk out basement to back yard and pool, 3 bedrooms (LL) to accommodate your guests, Large storage/mechanical room, Beautiful lawn and grounds to enhance your experience, Several large garages, pole buildings and horse shelter, 3 season gazebo with loft for additional summer time accommodations, Paved driveway with turn around for easy access, Well cared for residence, expertly maintained by original owner and family.  
You would love this place,  we do,  but we are 'up there' in age.

description: For sale: $236,900. Hand built log home privately nestled on a multi parcel wooded lot that is west facing. The interior features massive beams with custom metal work. 2+ Bedrooms. description: Recently sold: $309,000. Private and beautiful 4 bedroom/ 4 bath home located on Hill Lake, just South of Grand Rapids. Home is perfect for entertaining, as this home has an amazing open floor plan with stunning Western views, vaulted ceilings, towering windows and gorgeous brick fireplace.  A four season sun-room brings the outdoors inside.  Panoramic views of the lake from upper level bedrooms.  This unique property also features a lakeside mother-in-law suite or could be used as a separate living space, many possibilities.  Attached double, insulated garage and an additional 3 stall detached garage for all your lake home storage needs.
